The '''[[Fondor/Legends|Fondor]] Academy of Engineering and Design''' was a prime source of employee recruits for [[Kuat Drive Yards/Legends|Kuat Drive Yards]] and the [[Techno Union/Legends|Techno Union]] prior to the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. When the [[General Ministry Institutes|General Ministry Institute]] budget was cut, those two organizations began largely funding the Academy.

The academy was among the institutes associated with the [[New Republic General Ministry|General Ministry]] of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] government.<ref name="CTD">''[[Cracken's Threat Dossier]]''</ref>

